  "body": "<div align=\"center\">\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Cp3w8co.png\" height=\"400\"/>\n\n### Seamlessly integrate Create with Origins!\n\n_Adds recipes to Origins items, and allows for full automation_\n\n---\n\n<table align=\"center\">\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">\n<b>Currently recipes for these items:</b>\n</td>\n<td>\n\n- 👁️ **Orb of Origin**\n- ☂️ **Umbrella**\n</td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n\n---\n\n### 📦 Requirements\n\n<table align=\"center\">\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/create\">\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/Xbc0uyRg/icon.png\" width=\"32\"/>\n<br>\nCreate\n</a>\n</td>\n<td align=\"center\">\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/origins\">\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/3BeIrqZR/icon.png\" width=\"32\"/>\n<br>\nOrigins\n</a>\n</td>\n<td align=\"center\">\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/origins-umbrellas\">\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/nKWFvKt2/6c3b0c6406ecae007ef4a4bf3444bd4628809c70_96.webp\" width=\"32\"/>\n<br>\nOrigins Umbrellas <br>(optional)\n</a>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n\n---\n\n<div align=\"center\">\n<br>\n<i>Enhance your Origins experience with Create's mechanical wonders!</i>\n</div>\n\n[💬 Discord](https://discord.gg/rVuptEVnNd)\n\n<a href=\"https://bisecthosting.com/chillzone\" style=\"text-align:center; font-size: 20px; font-weight: bold;\">Need a server?</a>\n\n<a href=\"https://bisecthosting.com/chillzone\">\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/RQmshQt.png\" height=\"300\"/>\n</a>\n\n</div>\n",
